<h2 class="date">January 14, 2003</h2>


<div class="blogbody">
<a name="000001"></a>
<h3 class="title">Moving to MovableType</h3>

<p>For speed sake, I've decided to move over to MoveableType.</p>

<p>Postnuke was overkill for what I was doing. I love php and I love Postnuke but I figured this would be a better solution.</p>

<p>I'm a tinkerer. Always have been. I once ruined a clockradio by taking it apart then cutting the ends off the plug and sticking the individual wires in the socket.</p>

<p>Turns out a fuse had blown but I was only 9 so I had no clue. More fuses were blown after I was done with it.</p>

<p>I'll be migrating the stories over as soon as I can. Blogging is such a bad habit! And a bad word for that matter.</p>


<div class="posted">
	Posted by pugsly at <a href="http://www.lusis.org/mt/lusis/archives/3col-Ind.html">11:57 PM</a>
	
	
</div>

